          <fr:mainmatter>
 <fr:p>This is immediate, using the unit map of <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-0028.xml" title="Propositional truncation" addr="//erct/erct-0028" type="local">propositional truncation</fr:link> and the <fr:link href="foreign-erct-erct-000U.xml" title="Biinverse" addr="//erct/erct-000U" type="local">section</fr:link> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
